<%# 광고 — 시험 정보 하단 %>
<div class="py-4 px-4 bg-slate-50 flex justify-center border-t border-slate-100">
  <%= render 'shared/ad_slot', position: 'home-mid' %>
</div>

<!-- 2-2. 법령 체계도 섹션 -->
<section class="py-16 px-4 bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-100">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-10">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">account_tree</span>
        시험 필수 이해 — 법령 체계
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">공공조달 법령 체계도</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-xl mx-auto">국가계약법이 뿌리 법령입니다. 이 계층 구조를 이해하면<br>어떤 문제가 나와도 법령 간 연결고리로 정답을 찾을 수 있습니다.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 법령 트리 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 md:p-8">

      <!-- 뿌리: 국가계약법 -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-xl">gavel</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
            <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-base">국가계약법</span>
            <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 text-xs font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">뿌리 법령</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">국가를 당사자로 하는 계약의 기본 원칙 — 1과목 핵심</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 트리 구조 -->
      <div class="ml-6 border-l-2 border-slate-200 pl-4 mt-2 space-y-4">

        <!-- 지방계약법 -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -left-[1.35rem] top-3 w-4 border-t-2 border-slate-200"></div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 rounded-xl p-4">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-blue-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-base">account_balance</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 mb-1">
                <span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">지방계약법</span>
                <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-xs font-semibold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">95% 동일 → 차이점만 학습</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs">지방자치단체를 당사자로 하는 계약 규정. 국가계약법과 거의 동일하므로 차이점에 집중.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 조달사업법 -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -left-[1.35rem] top-3 w-4 border-t-2 border-slate-200"></div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-violet-50 border border-violet-100 rounded-xl p-4">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-violet-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-base">store</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 mb-1">
                <span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">조달사업법</span>
                <span class="text-slate-400 text-xs">국가계약법 + 지방계약법을 합산해 만든 법</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mb-3">조달청의 물자 구매·공급 사업 근거법. 나라장터 운영 기반.</p>

              <!-- 전자조달법 (하위) -->
              <div class="ml-4 border-l-2 border-violet-200 pl-3 space-y-2">
                <div class="relative">
                  <div class="absolute -left-[0.9rem] top-3 w-3 border-t-2 border-violet-200"></div>
                  <div class="bg-white border border-violet-200 rounded-lg p-3">
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 mb-1">
                      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-violet-500 text-base">computer</span>
                      <span class="font-semibold text-slate-700 text-sm">전자조달법</span>
                      <span class="text-slate-400 text-xs">조달사업법 실행을 위한 법</span>
                    </div>
                    <!-- 예규 (하위) -->
                    <div class="ml-5 border-l-2 border-slate-200 pl-3 mt-2 space-y-1.5">
                      <div class="relative">
                        <div class="absolute -left-[0.9rem] top-2 w-3 border-t-2 border-slate-200"></div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-600">
                          <span class="w-5 h-5 bg-indigo-100 rounded flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-indigo-500 text-xs">article</span>
                          </span>
                          <span><strong class="text-indigo-700">기재부 예규</strong> — 중앙조달 (국가기관)</span>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="relative">
                        <div class="absolute -left-[0.9rem] top-2 w-3 border-t-2 border-slate-200"></div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-600">
                          <span class="w-5 h-5 bg-teal-100 rounded flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-teal-500 text-xs">article</span>
                          </span>
                          <span><strong class="text-teal-700">행안부 예규</strong> — 지방조달 (지자체)</span>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="relative">
                        <div class="absolute -left-[0.9rem] top-2 w-3 border-t-2 border-slate-200"></div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-600">
                          <span class="w-5 h-5 bg-amber-100 rounded flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-amber-500 text-xs">shopping_cart</span>
                          </span>
                          <span><strong class="text-amber-700">다수공급자계약(MAS)</strong> — 나라장터 종합쇼핑몰</span>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 건설산업기본법 -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -left-[1.35rem] top-3 w-4 border-t-2 border-slate-200"></div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-rose-50 border border-rose-100 rounded-xl p-4">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-rose-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-base">construction</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 mb-1">
                <span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">건설산업기본법</span>
                <span class="bg-rose-100 text-rose-700 text-xs font-semibold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">공사계약 이해 필수</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs">공사계약을 논하려면 반드시 이해해야 하는 법령. 건설업 등록, 시공, 하도급 규정.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- 핵심 포인트 -->
      <div class="mt-6 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-xl px-5 py-4 flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-amber-500 text-lg flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">lightbulb</span>
        <p class="text-amber-800 text-sm">
          <strong>시험 전략:</strong> 법령을 단편적으로 외우지 말고 이 계층 구조를 먼저 이해하세요.
          어떤 법령이 왜 존재하는지 알면 생소한 문제도 흐름으로 정답을 추론할 수 있습니다.
        </p>
